    "en": {
      "title": "Three arrested for assaulting Deputy Inspector General of Police",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Three suspects have been arrested in the attack on Seresta Deputy Inspector General of Police Deshabandu Tennakon in charge of Western Province.",
        "The three suspects were arrested yesterday evening by the Colombo Crime Prevention Unit after the incident of the attack took place in Kollupitiya area on 10th May.",
        "It has been revealed that the three arrested persons are aged 31, 51 and 52 and belong to Pitapethara, Colombo-15.",
        "The suspects have been arrested on charges of obstruction of duty and violation of curfew."
      ],
